{CHARACTER_NAME}: JORDAN (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: So within months we started our own firm out of an abandoned auto body shop.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 36 INT. KACANDES DINER - DAY (OCT `88)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jordan sits with CHESTER MING, ROBBIE FEINBERG, ALDEN KUPFERBERG ("SEA OTTER") and BRAD, muscular and bald, with a Fu Manchu mustache.
