{DIALOGUE}: Give me them young, hungry and stupid and in no time I'll make them rich.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 40 EXT. MARINA - LONG ISLAND - SUNSET (MAY `89)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On lounge chairs at the edge of a dock, bottle of wine nearby, Jordan sits with Teresa.
