{CHARACTER_NAME}: TERESA
{DIALOGUE}: Omigod.
{DIALOGUE}: Jordan.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JORDAN
{DIALOGUE}: You like it?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TERESA
