{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jordan helps her try it on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She smiles, but he detects a wave of... something.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JORDAN
{DIALOGUE}: They're small, I know, but the stones are really high quality.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TERESA
{DIALOGUE}: No, no.
{DIALOGUE}: I love it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JORDAN
{DIALOGUE}: Then what?
