{CHARACTER_NAME}: CLIENT (O.S.)
{DIALOGUE}: It'll go up?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JORDAN
{DIALOGUE}: Exactly.
{DIALOGUE}: Which is why you should pick up 5000 shares today, a $200,000 investment.
