{DIALOGUE}: The Wolf of Wall Street Buff Revised Pages 3/5/13
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 58 INT. STRATTON OAKMONT II - BULLPEN - DAY (NOV `90)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: New offices now, a real brokerage firm.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bullpen is large, with 75 Brokers at polished maple desks, sitting before computers talking into headsets.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DONNIE
{DIALOGUE}: So the problem is that I don't have the luxury of a track record.
{DIALOGUE}: Sir, let me reintroduce myself to you.
{DIALOGUE}: My name is Donnie Azoff--
{META_DATA}: 58A CUT TO:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RUGRAT
