{CHARACTER_NAME}: PETER DEBLASIO
{DIALOGUE}: Peter DeBlasio from Stratton Oakmont in New York City--
{META_DATA}: 58D CUT TO:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TOBY WELCH
{DIALOGUE}: --and I plan on being the top broker in my firm this year.
{META_DATA}: 58E CUT TO:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SEA OTTER
{DIALOGUE}: So what about this?
{DIALOGUE}: We start small with 500 shares, a cash outlay of $20,000.
{META_DATA}: 58F CUT TO:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KALIL
{DIALOGUE}: If the stock goes up 10%, will that make you a rich man?
{DIALOGUE}: Of course not.
{META_DATA}: 58G CUT TO:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIMMIE BELZER
