{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Violet presses the garage door button.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Naomi grabs a tool and smashes the driver side window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jordan sees the door closing - he thinks "fuck it" - slams into reverse, crashing through the garage door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Car continues in reverse, crashing into a concrete pillar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Naomi and Violet rush to the car, pull Skylar out and bring her inside the house.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jordan sits as blood rushes down his face.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LUCAS SOLOMAN (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: Paragraph 1.
{DIALOGUE}: The defendant shall plead guilty to all counts of the indictment currently pending against him in the United States District Court for the Eastern District of New York.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 230D SCENES 230D - 230E OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 230F INT. U.S. ATTORNEY'S OFFICE - CONFERENCE ROOM - DAY
