{CHARACTER_NAME}: LUCAS SOLOMON
{DIALOGUE}: Paragraph 2.
{DIALOGUE}: The defendant shall provide information regarding all criminal activities of the defendant and others from June 1st, 1990, onwards.
{DIALOGUE}: Paragraph 3.
{DIALOGUE}: 131.
{DIALOGUE}: The Wolf of Wall Street Buff Revised Pages 3/5/13
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LUCAS SOLOMON (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: The defendant shall participate in undercover activities pursuant to the instructions of the FBI, including wearing a recording device, also known as a `wire', in conjunction with the investigation of securities fraud.
{DIALOGUE}: Paragraph 4.
{DIALOGUE}: The defendant must not commit, or attempt to commit, any further crimes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jordan's here, too, looking miserable.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stops Lucas.
