{DIALOGUE}: I hope your Honor would agree that Mr. Belfort has distinguished himself in terms of his cooperation in this white collar fraud.
{DIALOGUE}: Mr. Belfort has helped the government win convictions over two dozen serious offenders and helped them recover millions of dollars to be made available for restitution to the victims.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HON. RAYMOND SAMITZ
{DIALOGUE}: The sentence of the court shall be 48 months in Federal Prison.
{META_DATA}: (pause)
{DIALOGUE}: Please remand the defendant.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Max rolls his eyes: Jordan's so guilty it hurts.
